 swiperFotos()
 
+const swiperFotos = function(){
+  return swiper = new Swiper('.swiper-videos', {
+    // Default parameters
+    slidesPerView: 1,
+    spaceBetween: 10,
+    speed: 500,
+    autoplay: {
+      delay: 4000,
+    },
+    navigation: {
+        nextEl: '.swiper-button-next',
+        prevEl: '.swiper-button-prev',
+    },
+    // Responsive breakpoints
+    breakpoints: {
+      // when window width is >= 640px
+      640: {
+        slidesPerView: 1,
+        spaceBetween: 10,
+      },
+      pagination: {
+        el: '.swiper-pagination',
+      },    
+    }
+  })
+}
+
+swiperFotos()
+
